opt/gitlab/git-data/repositories\nGitLab Shell path:\t\t/opt/gitlab/embedded/service/gitlab-shell\nGit:\t\t/opt/gitlab/embedded/bin/git\n```\n\n## Impact\n\nAn attacker can:\n\n1. Perform any action within the application that a user can perform\n2. Steal sensitive user data\n3. Steal user's credentials","bounty_amount":"2000.0","formatted_bounty":"$2,000","weakness":{"id":62,"name":"Cross-site Scripting (XSS) - Stored"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":803617,"file_name":"1.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/FxxZDsTR2NdsTnEAmoW6N1n9?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%221.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%271.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQXG6W2HKE%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T083935Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIQCMt7Tu2%2Burv4UECBzNMPag02b0Nxq%2BIoP8Vpd5ZSYg%2FQIgCduj86AWWqau%2Bq%2B9KYVhNGBc7G7bCF%2Bp98ytqVgAU7cqugUI8f%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDFUSqHIOkXI%2FdY1eJCqOBZgwisrU2DzGzvl%2FhIFJTiasP2hw%2B1805cboOmOKUtkiNijJAtAeaDiJ2gFcupouKcfm%2F%2FeFl2IikMYSqfVKKxfvvEBsTkng%2F3tbk8b%2BtWqlJzUBkHjdQJsOtMUBKZdpKRz33Jv2smOFoduVhbpNMgmePfzJAv2LHta7EUs1YF3O13IAOoaOcEz2Proe1P7E%2Ff9FeXcBKaCiUJx2YCK6a9AKFvqbirRZfcQDtk2sBGLE0LX%2FdQFG5rfqSvLLnRMEPKpguoOFWFRyvZSTCfknYUOux77%2F8ncPWNzElzp6KStJE6U5Q9SLTU4lgB7YZm5Cz%2B2EfDdIQxn20aFHNWgDX2UixJjweG%2BczGV1HPJ9ryIfA5r2AW3wqjETNw9K3IDrF5du5VJpXHwQR2Pduk7pP7nFNGmWw8W4gcOCQOvISoxmBaOsQcBhS%2FKToMxyTJpzUCYEVBeosKsswxdVPR93ggVdUbhz589c6LjT3h26bjNrsOTLY20%2Bxud2B5ObrLF5sWUv6FHLGlRrmW0nV18%2FGkAI616gFxQsH420DIlY9aJsrUaIha9GEsUXJjFBGDWaixzhManWAj3bpglTfHSHHcCHqFJOXZnUg7j%2FBIAZrKg8dUR%2BH%2B3QHWsOC60QAPDh1H5GB235qQ4gfExcAN665H%2BZCxfehRhjOh5U0v%2F54n%2B2kbonB1ViyQpqH1eT8NgVuHB%2Fyl9QO0C4U%2Fijt3BAPIc%2FJ%2Fy